HEADWORD: Self-made
<hw>Self"-made`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Made by one's
self.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Self-made man</b></col>, <cd>a man who has risen from
poverty or obscurity by means of his own talents or
energies.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

